text: Class of 2020 Graduation

post_text:
Graduation ceremonies for the Union City High School Class of 2020 are on and will begin at 8 p.m. tonight at War Memorial Stadium.
The event will be broadcast via Facebook Live on the Union City Schools Facebook page.
Due to the COVID-19 pandemic, social distancing will be practiced for each of the 89 graduates, their permitted guests and UC School System personnel.
